François Maistre https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7ois_Maistre 0 François Maistre (14 May 1925 – 16 May 2016) was a French film, television and theatre actor. Born in Demigny, Saône-et-Loire, France, he appeared in nearly 100 films between 1960 and 2003. His father was singer and actor A.-M. Julien.
